swapExactETHForTokens(uint256,address[],.details: User specifies exact input (msg.value) and minimum output

params.amountOutMin: The minimum amount of tokens the user will accept
params.deadline: Unix timestamp after which the transaction will revert
params.path: Array of token addresses representing the swap path. First token must be WETH
params.to: Address that will receive the output tokens

returns.amounts: Array of amounts for each swap step:         - amounts[0] = ETH input amount         - amounts[amounts.length-1] = token output amount

swapTokensForExactETH(uint256,uint256,ad.details: User specifies maximum input and exact output

params.amountInMax: The maximum amount of tokens willing to spend
params.amountOut: The exact amount of ETH to receive
params.deadline: Unix timestamp after which the transaction will revert
params.path: Array of token addresses. Last address must be WETH
params.to: Address that will receive the ETH

returns.amounts: Array of amounts for each swap step:         - amounts[0] = token input amount         - amounts[amounts.length-1] = ETH output amount

swapExactETHForTokens(uint256,address[],.notice: Swaps an exact amount of ETH for tokens

swapTokensForExactETH(uint256,uint256,ad.notice: Swaps tokens for an exact amount of ETH
